  <description><![CDATA[<p>Set at the foot of the Pirin Mountains, Bansko attractively combines old town charm with a modern ski centre easily on a par with Western European resorts. Access the skiing via a 20 minute gondola ride, and climb above the tree line to enjoy the wonderful views and lovely snow conditions over 2500 metres. For après-ski most hotels provide excellent spa facilities for perfect relaxation, or wander through the cobbled streets of the old town to find Bansko's traditional tavernas, known as mehanas, and discover their warm and lively atmosphere.</p>
<p> </p>]]></description>
