  <generalInformation><![CDATA[<p><strong>Beginners skiing in Bansko</strong></p>
<p>First time skiers taking our value Learn to Ski package will enjoy the fun and supportive environment in which to master the basics</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Intermediate skiing in Bansko</strong></p>
<p>An ideal ski area with wide runs and varied terrain. A 16km run from Todorka Peak right through to the base gondola is sure to challenge even the fittest improver.</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Advanced skiing in Bansko</strong></p>
<p>Though not hugely spoilt for choice, the Alberto Tomba black run and several challenging reds will provide a good test.</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Snowboarding in Bansko</strong></p>
<p>Good access to all the pistes together with a fun park and half pipe to practice jumps and tricks.</p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>
<p> </p>]]></generalInformation>
